D,M,M',M''
A
0\rightarrow M' \rightarrow M \rightarrow M'' \rightarrow 0
f:M'\rightarrow M
g: M\rightarrow M''
0 \rightarrow Hom_A(M'',D) \rightarrow Hom_A(M,D) \rightarrow Hom_A(M',D)
f_{*} : Hom_A(M,D) \rightarrow Hom_A(M',D)
f_{*}(\phi) = \phi \circ f
\phi \in Hom_A(M,D)
g_{*} = \psi \circ g
\psi \in Hom_A(M'',D)
\ker(f_{*}) \subset Im(g_{*})
\phi \in \ker(f_{*}) \Rightarrow f_{*}( \phi) = 0 
 \phi \in Hom_A(M,D)
\Rightarrow  \phi \circ f = 0 \Rightarrow Im(f) \subset \ker(\phi)
\ker(g) \subset \ker(\phi)
\psi : M'' \rightarrow L
\psi \circ g = \phi
\psi = (\phi/\ker(g) ):M'' \rightarrow N
\bar{\phi}:M''\longrightarrow D
\phi
\bar{\phi}(y)=\phi(x)
y=g(x)
g_*(\bar{\phi})=\phi
\bar{\phi}
g(x)=y=g(z)
\phi(x)=\phi(z)
x-z\in\ker g
\ker g\subseteq \ker \phi
\phi(x-z)=0
\phi(x)=\phi(z)
g_*(\bar{\phi})=\bar{\phi}g
x\in M
\bar{\phi}(g(x))=\phi(x)
\bar{\phi}g=\phi
